Property Overrides
This sample demonstrates how to use &lt;DevicdSpecific&gt;
and &lt;Choice&gt; tags to override properties in a style on
a device-specific basis.
<p>
When viewed from an HTML browser, the form makes use of
typeface, color, and size to highlight content. 
On a WML phone, which doesn't have font features, 
the form uses italicized text.
